        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gaming-green/20 to-gaming-blue/20 rounded-3xl p-8 border border-gaming-green/30">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Join the Gaming Revolution</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
            Don't miss out on the best gaming content. Download EsportsStream today and discover what you've been missing.
          </p>
          <a href="#" class="bg-gaming-green text-dark-bg px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-gaming-green/90 transition-all transform hover:scale-105 inline-flex items-center space-x-2 animate-glow">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
